own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b198860a680ad6ffeae6e229a7b02785224a9951","tid":49494,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係歌頌 係美化黑社會嘅形象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解呢？"},{"pid":"8d70d696913f4abcfbc91e1b65e4458007cec586","tid":49494,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"電影發展基金(「發展基金」)最初於1999年成立，以資助有利香港電影業長遠發展的項目。<br />\n<br />\n*<br />\n<br />\n政府於2007年7月將3億元注入發展基金，並擴大其適用範疇，為中低成本的電影製作提供部分融資。政府於2015年5月再向發展基金注資2億港元，並在其下推出新計劃，資助製作預算不超過1,000萬港元的小型電影的製作經費。<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月，政府向發展基金額外注資2,000萬元，作為本地製作粵語電影在內地發行和宣傳費用的資助。<br />\n<br />\n*<br />\n<br />\n香港電影發展局秘書處負責管理發展基金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fdc.gov.hk/tc/services/services2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fdc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fservices%2Fservices2.htm&d=K8wAcjet1HEbSDaO5PBrvQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=68bf22a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fdc.gov.hk/tc/services/services2.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0f9baa1b7c8ebabe58778c10bc37c37dc43057b5","tid":49494,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:05:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74d7623d012fd33137b0ce9e7b328d3e13bb6732","tid":49494,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd62216d5986be5417f4b82e796bb5f3e93243e1","tid":49494,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"你睇下盲亨因為講過兩句人話，同埋撐過佔旺，就有班高登連登傻仔話衰唔晒，禍不及妻兒，就知道點解咁多人仲對黑社會有幻想啦！難怪咁多後生仔收人幾千走去走麵粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班老嘢就ff黑社會都有愛國嘅呢句(我老豆)"},{"pid":"3e93e7b6dc711d0ccab334394f3b39711c99487b","tid":49494,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20